This elastic plugin can be used to

    * update all or selected documents of an index, e.g. after you change the
      settings of a type
    * to change the index settings like shard count: create a new index with
      that config and reindex all documents into that index
    * grab all or selected documents from another elasticsearch cluster and
      feed your local machine with that
    * and more like a filtered backup etc
    * See ExampleUsage.java on how to use this plugin as simple rewriter of
      your content

WWW: https://github.com/karussell/elasticsearch-reindex
